    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/223a18-2/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=577447451649115027&sectionId=577447451716486035)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggd6agp_vR8_text","label":"ggd6agp_vR8_text","default":"4. It rewrites the rules of what a “luxury mask” feels like"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSTMMh343s_text","label":"ggSTMMh343s_text","default":"<p>There’s nothing flashy here—no gold dust or influencer gimmicks. Just a jelly-like texture that <strong>cools, calms, and clings gently to the skin without sliding off.</strong>&nbsp;It feels instantly soothing and indulgent without being over-the-top. It’s the kind of mask you look forward to using. <strong>Quiet luxury, in the best way.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggczeYX6lJK_text","label":"ggczeYX6lJK_text","default":"5. It’s gaining popularity without influencer hype — and that says something"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmUMHmlfzt_text","label":"ggmUMHmlfzt_text","default":"<p>This isn’t a product you’ll find all over your feed, and <strong>that’s exactly why I trust it.</strong>&nbsp;The women who use it are reordering it long before they run out. It’s become a quiet staple in circles that value efficacy over flash. When a product builds loyalty without buzz, that says something.&nbsp;<strong>Word of mouth made this a staple in my routine.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkmtPJdmK0_text","label":"ggkmtPJdmK0_text","default":"6. It defies the myth that aging skin can’t handle real results"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1IqMe2L0w_text","label":"gg1IqMe2L0w_text","default":"<p>Many anti-aging products either underperform or overwhelm. <strong>This one finds the balance.</strong> It firms without irritating, calms without dulling, and <strong>gives you results that feel respectful of where your skin is now.</strong>&nbsp;There’s no pretending you’re 25.&nbsp;<strong>There’s just healthy, vibrant skin that looks like you’ve been taking care of yourself for years.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj5jQ2fe-n_text","label":"ggj5jQ2fe-n_text","default":"7. It turns one-off results into a weekly ritual you’ll actually keep"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDESzWhN1y_text","label":"ggDESzWhN1y_text","default":"<p>This mask isn’t a one-time miracle.&nbsp;<strong>It’s a weekly ritual that your skin actually responds to — fewer dry patches, a little more glow, a lot more bounce.</strong>&nbsp;And the bundles are thoughtfully structured for&nbsp;<strong>real use: monthly, weekly, even daily if needed.</strong> It fits into your life without demanding too much. And honestly, <strong>that kind of practicality is what keeps me coming back.</strong></p>"}],
